		<h1>
		
		
			Buildings and clothes could melt to save energy
		
		</h1>
		<ul class="markerlist">
		<li>
		
		
			
			
				05 January 2012
			
		

		 by
			
				
					<a href="/search?rbauthors=Phil+McKenna"><b>Phil McKenna</b></a>
				
				
				
			
		
		</li>
		
					<li>Magazine issue <a href="/issue/2846">2846</a>.  <a href="/subscribe?promcode=nsarttop"><b>Subscribe and save</b></a></li>
		
		
			<li>
			For similar stories, visit the
				
					
						<a href="/topic/energy-fuels"><b>Energy and Fuels</b></a>
					
					
					
					
